Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真啰嗦 老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.64,0:00:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}皋月！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.31,0:00:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不可理喻！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.30,0:00:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那个死老太…什么都不懂！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.17,0:00:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老太婆…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.75,0:00:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:00:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}死老太婆！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.18,0:00:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}受不了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}拍了张不错的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你就这么随便拍？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.03,0:02:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我只要看到美丽的东西就会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.84,0:02:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}也算是我们摄影师的性情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.82,0:02:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}大叔 你可真够恶心的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真打击人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我还觉得姑且该算是你哥哥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.26,0:02:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你要不要买下我？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我想要储备用来离家出走的资金
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}敬谢不敏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.15,0:03:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}再怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我还是没有对穿着运动内衣的女孩子出手的勇气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.21,0:04:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}给我便宜点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}说的也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.18,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那这个数怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.89,0:04:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这个价钱已经很超值了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}100日元？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好贵啊 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是吗 大叔我好歹也是专业的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.42,0:04:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}从这里开始就是重头戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绪花？就是那个小鬼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要是那家伙做主角那我还是不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.35,0:04:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.54,0:04:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}听好了 绪花的优点可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}越是细细咀嚼细心品尝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就越能感受到饱含其中的精…华
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}能承蒙您如此赞美 真是感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}糟糕了 是绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真人还是算了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.54,0:05:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真人还是算了…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.08,0:05:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是的 绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.65,0:05:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}居然这么妨碍我工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.31,0:05:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这个是！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}「经历苦难！新人招待小姐诞生！」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}难得写下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以就姑且就把它拿来出租了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.95,0:05:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}出租！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}为了直接把作品展现给理解这份创作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}并对作品满怀期待的读者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}听好了 出租图书的历史课是很深奥的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}它的起源得从那著名的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是的 居然还在写这种东西 真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.89,0:06:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我想变得更加闪耀！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}想要变得闪耀…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.63,0:06:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好了 赶紧回去努力工作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.73,0:06:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}明白了 您辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.48,0:06:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}虽说是施工停电 但也就3小时而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}为了不给客人添麻烦 希望您尽早完工
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.23,0:06:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不知道在我有生之年能不能开发出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}依靠无谓的干劲就能发电的技术啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.93,0:07:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我在喜翠荘的生活已经成为了「日常」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}感觉工作也都做得比较顺手了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}最初「想要变得闪耀」的想法却有些许褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这一带因为我经常擦拭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}应该算是挺闪亮了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.31,0:07:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这是什么？好像人的脸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.45,0:07:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要不要帮你把额头也擦得锃亮锃亮的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.71,0:07:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就擦这点地方也没用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.77,0:07:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}居然有台阶太犯规啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结名！？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.90,0:08:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}莲叔 这个也要用上吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.28,0:08:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没错 因为这些腐败得快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以先把这些容易变质的食材都过一下火吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这边的鱼就做成甘露煮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}蹄膀已经解冻了 就做成炖肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}这个就用酱油…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.64,0:08:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结名…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是彻和鹤来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不可以打扰人家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这个剪平头的人叫啥来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你竟敢对莲叔这么无礼…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}鲜鲷鱼片 好吓人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.42,0:08:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不过如果往这里装饰上蒲公英就好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结名…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}好了哦 ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.88,0:08:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}生·鱼·片 Pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.88,0:08:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}滚出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:58.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}给…给我滚出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结名
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}人家是来这边做老板娘修行的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.13,0:09:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以有很多东西都想学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.37,0:09:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.36,0:09:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}在喜翠荘进行修行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.08,0:09:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.93,0:09:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}而且是秋季连休限定版~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}福屋的老板娘已经拜托我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}说想让她也学习一下其他旅馆的作风
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}作风…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小女子不才 请多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老…老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.60,0:09:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那就交给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}给…给我？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}为什么啊… 老板娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.40,0:09:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}交给你了 绪花~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}感觉被搪塞了一件十分麻烦的差事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不要在意！绪花！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.13,0:09:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}谢…谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.35,0:09:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}接下来~去别的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结名 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.07,0:10:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20\an8}上一周经过日本海的11号台风…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.52,0:10:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好了 开始会议吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.84,0:10:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}停电的事情在预约的时候已经说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.92,0:10:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}总之端出茶点的时候再提醒一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.45,0:10:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}还有男女澡堂使用时间也有变更
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}唔 在端出茶点的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.09,0:10:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}反正就早上几小时还是有办法应付的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}而且客人们大概也到附近散步之类的去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.50,0:10:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不行不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}居然说什么应付
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.74,0:10:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}得好好为客人们着想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.92,0:10:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}请你们要像接待未婚夫那样既温柔 又甜蜜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}像接待未婚夫那样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我的一切都属于你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}若是为了你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.06,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}哪怕赴汤蹈火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对吧 崇子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.19,0:10:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对于没有对象的巴姐来说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}想必很难理解这份独特的情感吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这时候就用你那剩女独有的妄想能力来弥补吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}巴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那是什么破烂肥皂剧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可恶 开什么玩笑 混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.54,0:11:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}巴姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}反正我就是不懂那种热恋情怀啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}根本就是未知的世界嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.22,0:11:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.65,0:11:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}够了 反正我还有深爱着的工作陪伴我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那什么狗屁未婚夫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}讨厌~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}怎么弄都弄不好啦 又起皱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}把它绷直铺开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}来 把这个角压好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.84,0:11:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}然后像这样子 用手掌把它铺开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.68,0:12:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.85,0:12:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}做得不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}巴姐真会教人啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真厉害 您小孩有这么温柔的母亲可真幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小孩？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.40,0:12:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我看您总是这么沉着冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就想您是不是已经当妈妈啦…我猜错了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}别说什么母亲了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我现在就连怀上孩子的前提条件都还没有啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是的 你这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那可是巴姐最脆弱的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.44,0:12:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那结衣 你就把这些旧浴衣收到这里吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.14,0:12:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不好 差点忘记床单快洗完了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你赶紧过去瞧瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}只是收浴衣这种小事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}交给结衣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.77,0:12:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不用在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.32,0:13:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是吗 那就顺便把剩下的地板也擦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}多多指教~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.06,0:13:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不过 这都是些不起眼的杂活呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.80,0:13:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结名想做些更厉害的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜 真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.42,0:13:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜 你看上去好像挺疲惫的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是有一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我父母现在都去进修了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.09,0:14:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你父母好像是老师来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真不容易啊 家务活现在都自己做吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对啊 不过也就是比平常累一点点而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}后天麻奈…我妹妹她要去郊游挖白薯呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.37,0:14:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}挖白薯…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.89,0:14:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯 郊游
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}一开始妈妈说能请到假的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}她当时好开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.18,0:14:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}现在肯定很失望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.61,0:14:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这种感觉我明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}正所谓期望越高 失望越大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那种失望感 无论过了多少年也难以忘怀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}难…难道我把你越说越难受了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不过没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:15:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}反正渐渐就不当回事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对于家庭幸福这种东西越来越没有期望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}然后也能找到一条自己的人生道路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.35,0:15:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我也是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对…对不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.07,0:15:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这是小菜脆弱的地方吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}莲叔 咸烹海味已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.34,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我说啊 彻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.00,0:15:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我是不是别剪平头比较好啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}炖肉我也开始弄了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.49,0:15:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.05,0:15:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没事 这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}民子 你那边进展如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯…已经好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.78,0:15:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}让我尝一尝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好… 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}怎…怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}明天预约的是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}记得好像有一家是带着小孩的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20\an8}还有一家是来庆祝八十大寿的夫妇…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这样子肯定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}莲叔 甘露煮就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}记得出锅时蜂蜜不要放得太多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.14,0:16:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.53,0:16:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜真了不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不仅家务全部一手包办
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}还那么关心妹妹的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜…真像一位母亲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}而且还是十分理想的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我家的家庭关系就有点…或者是说非常奇怪呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小时候还是有好多事情满怀期待
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}渐渐地 就连那点事情都不再抱有期望
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我并不讨厌妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈她不了解我的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.34,0:17:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但实际上 我也不了解妈妈是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不行~这个真是太好玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这样子如何啊 老爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.01,0:17:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那…那个 差不多该换我了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}真想弄得更加有独创性呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}剪成心形也许会很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.42,0:17:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那样…我会很困扰的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.47,0:17:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结名她到底有没有收拾好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}一片惨状啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.29,0:17:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这到底是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.89,0:17:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这是…豆丁爷写的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.66,0:18:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}庭院的红叶 三分红
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}三好夫妇入住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}伙食 猪肉酱汤和羊栖菜饭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}连这些东西也都记下来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}「我想要闪耀」皋月这么说道？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.39,0:18:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老板娘 椿之间的客人可能会迟点才到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}亚纪 波之间的打扫工作已经完成了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.25,0:18:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.25,0:18:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老板娘 鹤之间的客人想就明天早餐和您谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我马上就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈…我要吃零食
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}去跟皋月要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.97,0:18:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但… 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.96,0:18:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}缘？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你要去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.31,0:19:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}去和朋友开学习会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那谁来照顾缘？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我要考试 哪有时间照顾这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}皋月！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.52,0:19:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不要吵架啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我… 我不吃零食就是了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老板娘！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.26,0:19:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没事的 只是站着有点犯晕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.15,0:19:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}请不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}昨天也是 都已经很晚了 房间里的灯还亮着…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}电六你既然知道这些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.46,0:20:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就说明你昨天也工作到很晚了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.85,0:20:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老板死后喜翠庄也变了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.30,0:20:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}果然老板娘就是不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.77,0:20:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我不想被人这么评价
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.47,0:20:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}罪犯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}擅自乱拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}汤乃鹭真的是个不错的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}自然未经雕琢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.32,0:20:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}女孩子也很淳朴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}忍不住就照了下来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.32,0:20:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你的意思是说我土里土气的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}的确 年轻人会说土里土气这种话还真让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.80,0:20:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}想去东京上大学吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}比起去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.40,0:21:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我只是想远离那个家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}远离那个家？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}待在那里感觉自己好像要腐烂了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我想让自己更加闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你就是现在也闪耀着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.88,0:21:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}下一班列车要等30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.08,0:22:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那男人什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}很帅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}一般吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}感觉挺靠不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你可省着点吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.02,0:22:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这不是你迟到的惩罚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.96,0:22:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我说你啊 要买这么激情四射的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.58,0:22:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}5000日元！？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.74,0:22:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}钱没带够 借我点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.00,0:22:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}皋月…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.46,0:22:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你不是去开学习会了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.88,0:22:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.24,0:22:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这是我用自己的零用钱买的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.92,0:22:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}和你有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你以为你的零用钱是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}买这种艳俗的内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.98,0:22:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是丢人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}东京的学生都穿这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我也要去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那你去东京又打算做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.82,0:23:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没有目标没有梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.84,0:23:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}整天嚷嚷着要去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.94,0:23:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这事情才没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.44,0:23:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我想要变得闪耀！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可是…可是在这里没办法做到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.96,0:23:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我不想变得和妈妈一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}被过往缠住
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.02,0:23:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}为爸爸的亡灵所困
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}然后再为此拼尽全力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.06,0:23:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}简直像个笨蛋一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.66,0:23:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.06,0:23:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绝对不成为妈妈这种人！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.72,0:23:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绝对不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.90,0:23:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}皋月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.40,0:23:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}「摄影师」长期住宿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.00,0:23:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}「皋月 被打了两巴掌」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.68,0:24:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}写得粗粗拉拉的看不太懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.00,0:24:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.38,0:24:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈原来也想要闪耀过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.90,0:24:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}而且…这个摄影师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.46,0:24:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}一定就是爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.16,0:24:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}两个人就是在这里邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.54,0:24:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}而我就是在这段时间出生的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.12,0:24:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an9}{\fad(0,100)}很抱歉没能去送你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.12,0:24:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an9}{\fad(0,100)}绪花、加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}再见…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.96,0:24:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}今天很开心！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.92,0:24:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.70,0:24:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那人到底在搞什么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.72,0:24:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}净给我生乱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.22,0:24:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}本来就因为停电忙得手忙脚乱了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.00,0:25:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}民子也要用用看不
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.64,0:25:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那是用在哪的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.52,0:25:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.66,0:25:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.42,0:25:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}用它就能将脚底硬硬的角质给…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.44,0:25:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我妈妈的脚底也有这种厚厚硬硬的黄色…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.54,0:25:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}角质的厚度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.94,0:25:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可说明了辛苦劳动的分量啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.74,0:25:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你们的锻炼还不够！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.54,0:25:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.60,0:25:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.44,0:25:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜今天没来泡澡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.72,0:25:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是去照顾弟弟们了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.46,0:25:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.90,0:25:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}干完工作又要开工
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.40,0:26:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜真是很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.72,0:26:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}与其说像大人 更像是妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.54,0:26:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}会不会变黄呢…脚底
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.40,0:26:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.00,0:26:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.78,0:26:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.48,0:26:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}打嗝了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.82,0:26:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}有人在说闲话啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.00,0:26:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}笨蛋 说闲话是打喷嚏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.44,0:26:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.40,0:26:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}怎么啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.34,0:26:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}想吓吓你嘛 吓吓
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.68,0:26:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.66,0:26:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}像这样把头低下喝点水就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.84,0:26:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈也要试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.82,0:26:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}试试 试试
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.02,0:26:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}试吧试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.38,0:26:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}给
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.06,0:26:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.48,0:26:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}搞砸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.88,0:26:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}湿漉漉的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.26,0:26:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是的 别给我增加工作量啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.26,0:27:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.42,0:27:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我在想后天郊游我要不要也请个假
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.58,0:27:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.78,0:27:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以跟姐姐一起去郊游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.00,0:27:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.90,0:27:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.72,0:27:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.96,0:27:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好棒~
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.98,0:27:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真好啊 麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.20,0:27:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}接下来 正确答案是…哪个！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.08,0:27:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这个月开销有点多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.42,0:27:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}买了新的不能用也挺可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.80,0:27:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}菜子 读连环画
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.04,0:27:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好啊 等等哦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.40,0:27:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.72,0:27:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}菜子已经很累了让她休息会儿啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.20,0:27:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.38,0:27:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.62,0:27:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}公主对王子说
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.04,0:28:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那不是茶碗而是茶壶
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.52,0:28:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.12,0:28:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}还没睡着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.02,0:28:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.38,0:28:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小民好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.04,0:28:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.38,0:29:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你要回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.88,0:29:06.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}毕竟在这待了很长时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.30,0:29:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好照片也拍了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.74,0:29:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.86,0:29:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你接下来不是要来东京念书吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.88,0:29:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我对妈妈说了很过分的话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.88,0:29:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}说了想要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.24,0:29:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就这样要去东京
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.96,0:29:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可出钱的还是妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.42,0:29:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}还说什么想要闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.26,0:29:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可到底来什么也没想好
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.92,0:29:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}去东京到底想做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.78,0:29:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要不要来我这坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.70,0:29:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}有点乱别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.78,0:30:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.54,0:30:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这个
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.10,0:30:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不对…这不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.08,0:30:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我没有这么闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.68,0:30:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但这是从我眼中看到的皋月
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.68,0:30:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}自己的闪耀之处自己是很难看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.04,0:30:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}并不是非要到达终点才能够闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.54,0:30:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}即便是经历各种烦恼纠结
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.40,0:30:34.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这样的过程
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.10,0:30:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你看…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.92,0:30:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}也是如此的美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.64,0:30:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}皋月 怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.48,0:30:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我可能喜欢上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.62,0:30:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.12,0:31:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你大概只是把对于东京的憧憬和对我的感情搅在一起罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.60,0:31:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}装什么大人样！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.28,0:31:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.04,0:31:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就在装！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.66,0:31:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}讨…讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.22,0:31:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.34,0:31:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.56,0:31:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.02,0:31:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}人家要走了哦 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.20,0:31:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没事 小缘
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.10,0:31:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}能帮我把这个交给你姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.84,0:31:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}跟她说是她忘了的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.16,0:31:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.84,0:31:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.82,0:31:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.62,0:31:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}姐姐嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.16,0:32:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.82,0:32:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我才不会让你说什么再见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.36,0:32:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好的 我会替您传达
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.08,0:32:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}有客人…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.84,0:32:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老板娘 从小姐的学校来了电话…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.38,0:33:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}皋月 我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.68,0:33:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}刚才学校来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.32,0:33:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}说是你更改了志愿学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.14,0:33:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你擅自做什么决定
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.50,0:33:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我找到到自己想要做的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.06,0:33:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我要成为编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.32,0:33:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我将来想和那个人一起工作
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.02,0:33:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.64,0:33:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你想要做的事就是追着男人的屁股跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.74,0:33:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不是和妈妈你一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.30,0:33:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}追在爸爸的后面
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.38,0:33:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但我不否定这点了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.96,0:33:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.30,0:33:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}让我去东京吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.98,0:33:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}生活费我会靠打工想办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.54,0:33:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}请允许我…去追梦吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.50,0:33:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}找到…想要做的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.62,0:33:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈 找到了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.70,0:33:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.50,0:34:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}觉得心儿扑通扑通的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.14,0:34:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.66,0:34:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈也有寻找过想做的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.50,0:34:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}然后她好像…找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.60,0:34:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}虽然这也是理所当然的事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.12,0:34:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但从我懂事起妈妈就有大人的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.30,0:34:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}而且还是个乱七八糟的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.12,0:34:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}完全不知道她在想什么
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.44,0:34:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}也没法跟她较劲
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.34,0:34:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但依然是个大人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.92,0:34:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}像妈妈这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.48,0:34:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}竟然也有跟我一样想要闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.20,0:34:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}想要寻找什么的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.34,0:34:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}怎么办…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.52,0:34:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}哎 又搞晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.94,0:34:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}糟了 手机…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.28,0:34:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.52,0:35:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}彻先生
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.24,0:35:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你这么晚在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.66,0:35:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}在跑步
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.22,0:35:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这我一看就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.96,0:35:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就是觉得有点兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.98,0:35:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}兴奋？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.82,0:35:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.50,0:35:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那再见啦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.06,0:35:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我觉得心潮澎湃
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.62,0:35:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}原本觉得是离我那么遥远的大人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.82,0:35:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈她也在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.30,0:35:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}烦恼过
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.30,0:35:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}迷茫过
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.50,0:35:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}恋爱过
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.58,0:35:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}恋爱…过？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.56,0:35:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.04,0:35:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}邂逅了爱情
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.92,0:35:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我明明也…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.82,0:35:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}邂逅过
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.54,0:35:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绪花 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.26,0:36:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是隔壁班的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.54,0:36:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我们又不是那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.78,0:36:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我可不想给人家误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.12,0:36:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小孝？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.22,0:36:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.32,0:36:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那里空出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.48,0:36:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}正好在樱花下面
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.80,0:36:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}然而我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.64,0:36:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.34,0:36:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我想做出能够得到彻认可的菜
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.04,0:36:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.02,0:36:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}咸烹海味Pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.16,0:37:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}女人一到晚上都会打鸡血吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.92,0:37:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.84,0:37:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}早安
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.38,0:37:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}早
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.54,0:37:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}莲叔
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.60,0:37:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你的头发…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.74,0:37:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯…偶尔剪下
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.62,0:37:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}算是换…个形象？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.12,0:37:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.86,0:38:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没时间了也要好好整理下
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.78,0:38:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.22,0:38:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}听好了 莲叔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.78,0:38:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我们今后的路还远着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.44,0:38:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可不能松懈哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.72,0:38:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}今天可要拼命努力直到脚底生出一层厚厚的角质为止哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.38,0:38:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.72,0:38:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}脚底…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.28,0:38:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}角质？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.16,0:38:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.76,0:38:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那结名先去打扫房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.42,0:38:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要用这个哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.96,0:38:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.96,0:38:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}已经到点停电啦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.18,0:38:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.06,0:38:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}从九点开始 真不愧是结名
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.94,0:38:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}已经过了十分钟了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.92,0:38:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}大家的份也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.28,0:38:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结名好聪明
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.90,0:38:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结名我啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.96,0:38:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可正处于成长期哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.28,0:38:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.56,0:38:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}在各方面！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.88,0:38:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}都有成长的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.32,0:38:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}给我看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.20,0:39:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.16,0:39:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}巴姐抹布擦地 难得一见啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.34,0:39:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}已经开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.12,0:39:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好吧 趁现在把能做的事先做好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.20,0:39:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}伙食准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.68,0:39:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.92,0:39:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}现在可没工夫慢慢吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.48,0:39:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我们就在这里吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.82,0:39:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.22,0:39:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好的 我去拿
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.64,0:39:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}还是先去和供货商沟通一下吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.06,0:39:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.48,0:39:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}毕竟在停电期间 提前问一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.14,0:39:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.08,0:39:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.92,0:39:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这可是我通宵想出来的自信作品
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.42,0:39:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}靠这个彻就能认可我了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.08,0:39:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.64,0:39:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}哦？这真是花心思了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.42,0:39:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}该怎么吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.38,0:39:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这个就是把它按口味放在法式面包…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.62,0:39:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.54,0:39:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}莲叔
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.98,0:39:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}进货的时间还得说说
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.70,0:39:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我趁现在去联络一下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.94,0:39:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯 早饭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.00,0:39:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}一会儿再吃
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.64,0:39:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那边弄完之后 桐之间就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.58,0:40:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.08,0:40:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}是啊 之前…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.86,0:40:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结名 来这边搭把手
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.90,0:40:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.48,0:40:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}看来挺合得来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.70,0:40:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}呼~完事
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.52,0:40:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结衣也挺卖劲儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.50,0:40:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}应该能照常收工
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.50,0:40:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯 因为没电我还担心了好一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.86,0:40:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}能顺利解决实在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.62,0:40:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}毕竟明天要去郊游 我还想早点回去准备呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.60,0:40:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你可以回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.24,0:40:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我会把小菜的份一起做掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.32,0:40:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶 这样不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.86,0:40:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没事 反正就一天
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.20,0:40:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}而且差不多也该来电了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.56,0:41:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶！？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.96,0:41:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.88,0:41:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这一带停电施工已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.76,0:41:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但因为施工车辆出了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.44,0:41:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以只有喜翠庄的附近还没来电…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.40,0:41:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}事故？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.52,0:41:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我们会继续努力施工
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.30,0:41:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但是还得再等一会儿才能恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.40,0:41:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你们怎么能这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.16,0:41:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这种事情也无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.16,0:41:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}谋事在人成事在天
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.08,0:41:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.00,0:41:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.84,0:41:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你们的脑袋是长着做摆设的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.14,0:41:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要绞尽脑汁 想办法度过这道难关
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.84,0:41:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}莲先生 厨房的情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.88,0:41:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}如果烤炉不能用的话就烧窑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.02,0:41:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}然后把菜单换成炭火烤的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.40,0:41:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要是冰箱能用倒还好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.92,0:41:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可现在这情况蔬菜冻是做不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.70,0:41:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就煮成清淡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.60,0:42:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}巴 去跟客人说明一下情况
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.42,0:42:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}另外再去准备一下紧急发电机
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.24,0:41:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜 要回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.40,0:42:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}现在这样我怎么可能一个人回去
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.42,0:42:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我也得好好加油才行
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.10,0:42:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.14,0:42:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.72,0:42:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是的 什么事啊智也
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.68,0:42:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}都跟你说了除非万不得已别打给我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.20,0:42:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}因为…就是…万不得已了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.24,0:42:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈不见了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.52,0:42:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.60,0:42:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我帮她准备明天郊游的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.26,0:42:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可她态度很臭…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.12,0:42:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}等等 这是什么时候的事
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.24,0:42:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}3…30分钟前
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.10,0:42:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我去找了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.24,0:42:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}阿缘？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.24,0:42:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\pos(622,651)}Anything
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.74,0:42:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.92,0:42:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}菜子
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.82,0:42:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.38,0:42:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}现在反正都这样了 你们走一个还是两个都没差
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.12,0:42:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就跟她一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.08,0:42:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.50,0:42:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老板娘…可现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.50,0:42:59.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好了大伙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.34,0:43:00.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}都回到自己的位置上去
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.12,0:43:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}大家一起合力度过这道难关吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.34,0:43:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.24,0:43:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.76,0:43:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.10,0:43:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.70,0:43:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.28,0:43:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.46,0:43:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.84,0:43:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.66,0:43:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没有…我还以为她肯定会在这里的…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.80,0:43:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}继续找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.06,0:43:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}她还会去哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.22,0:43:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}喂 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.16,0:43:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你说什么？给警察打电话了？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.28,0:43:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈你不来又有什么用！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.48,0:43:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我一定会找到麻奈的
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.42,0:43:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}然后你再陪我们一起去郊游吧
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.64,0:44:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}工作的事情怎样都好！你也回来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.54,0:44:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小…小菜
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.58,0:44:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我平常不都很听话吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.90,0:44:07.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}很听话的…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.96,0:44:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但至少现在听听我的话好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.26,0:44:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我一直都很忍耐了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.90,0:44:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但现在…就让我任性一回好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.72,0:44:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}回来啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.84,0:44:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.28,0:44:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我已经忍了…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.98,0:44:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没错…忍了好多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.98,0:44:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈晚上出去玩我也忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.36,0:44:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好黑…一个人好害怕我也忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.02,0:44:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an9}妈妈讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.04,0:44:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}即便如此我还是忍过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.40,0:44:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}参观上课
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.36,0:44:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}去动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.38,0:44:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}去游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.36,0:44:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就是你都说没法我也忍下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.14,0:44:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈你总说自己工作忙
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.96,0:44:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}上次你也说好要跟麻奈去商场的屋顶玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.80,0:44:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结果还不是毁约了！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.46,0:45:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}她可是…好期待的…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.42,0:45:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.60,0:45:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈可能在那边
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.76,0:45:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我也有过这样的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.26,0:45:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈本来说要和我去动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.56,0:45:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}结果毁约了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.16,0:45:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可是我不甘心…又不知道怎么去
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.08,0:45:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以就去了宠物店
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.86,0:46:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.08,0:46:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.36,0:46:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.84,0:46:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈你这个笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.32,0:46:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}为什么要自己乱跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.88,0:46:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可是…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.22,0:46:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}笨蛋！明天不是要去郊游吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.96,0:46:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要是不能去了怎么…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.02,0:46:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我不想去！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.56,0:47:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}如果…如果妈妈不一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.12,0:47:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那郊游…有什么好去…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.28,0:47:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}大家都是跟妈妈一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.08,0:47:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我才不想自己去！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.30,0:47:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}还有姐姐在
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.86,0:47:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}姐姐会陪你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.40,0:47:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}便当里会放好多好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.02,0:47:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.12,0:47:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以要乖
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.54,0:47:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}怎么了…绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.96,0:47:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我也不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.56,0:47:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}因为小菜你不哭…我才替你哭的…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.98,0:48:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜你自己也还是个小孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.08,0:48:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}却说什么大人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.90,0:48:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜你自己也很想哭吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.34,0:48:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可你真的好伟大
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.46,0:48:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}能好好当个「大人」
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.38,0:48:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绪花…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.84,0:48:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我跟智也打过电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.22,0:48:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}帮我跟他说对不起了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.00,0:48:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.80,0:48:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但麻奈你自己也要道歉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.94,0:48:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好~
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.98,0:48:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}雪洞？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.94,0:49:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好漂亮！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.96,0:49:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这些全都是蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.76,0:49:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你们回来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.78,0:49:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你妹妹也一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.28,0:49:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.52,0:49:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那…那个 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.00,0:49:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}用烛光夜晚挺过停电的主意很棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.00,0:49:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\pos(460,654)\fs36}candle night
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.70,0:49:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.72,0:49:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那边也要放点
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.48,0:49:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这点子是她想出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.04,0:49:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶 结名想的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.40,0:49:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}客人们可开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.14,0:49:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}虽然也有莲叔他们努力做菜的功劳
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.34,0:49:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但客人们可是赞不绝口 还说没电反而更好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.52,0:49:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那边也有
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.00,0:49:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.16,0:49:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是个可怕的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.64,0:49:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}她身上可能有负责招待的神明附身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.48,0:49:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}负…负责招待的神明
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.70,0:49:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}骚乱一场非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.20,0:50:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你为什么不提前告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.62,0:50:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}如果父母不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.22,0:50:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就没必要勉强自己出来工作
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.62,0:50:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可…可是停电了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.86,0:50:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}大家都忙得不可开交…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.00,0:50:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}考虑太多反倒添了麻烦该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.16,0:50:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}别欺负菜子！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.92,0:50:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.46,0:50:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.36,0:50:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.46,0:50:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}放开我！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.58,0:50:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}去泡个澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.54,0:50:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}毛巾水母！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.24,0:50:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.26,0:50:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我先出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.72,0:50:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}辛苦啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.36,0:50:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好舒服…
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.66,0:50:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好累啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.94,0:50:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对不起啊 给你们添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.36,0:50:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不是…跟那个没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.16,0:50:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}喂 麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.28,0:50:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不要在澡堂玩水
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.94,0:50:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我也要游~
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.78,0:51:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}还真是吵闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.02,0:51:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.60,0:51:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}姐姐还没数到一百就出去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.52,0:51:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}吵死了 缘你这只黑猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.20,0:51:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妖怪~
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.96,0:51:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妖怪妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.22,0:51:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈 先穿上内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.38,0:51:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.60,0:51:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}狡猾！麻奈也要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.02,0:51:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}给
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.22,0:51:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.56,0:51:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈来的讯息
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.08,0:51:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}说她也可以去郊游
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.86,0:51:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.70,0:51:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.26,0:51:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.60,0:51:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}太好啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.30,0:51:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是的 内裤穿好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.30,0:51:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}菜子 要做便当哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.24,0:51:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要像新年那样一层一层的！
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.24,0:51:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}一层一层？那种现在来不及做啦
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.40,0:52:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}诶 麻奈要一层一层的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.50,0:52:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}我也会帮忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.94,0:52:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.72,0:52:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}得还回去才行
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.82,0:52:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}已经没写关于妈妈的事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.60,0:52:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}也是
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.18,0:52:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这会儿妈妈已经到东京去了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.44,0:52:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈的事情大概是不会写在这里面了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.22,0:52:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈一开始也不是大人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.02,0:52:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}别说是如何去闪耀…恐怕连恋爱也不明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.18,0:52:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}慢慢经历各种各样的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.32,0:52:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}然后才…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.92,0:52:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.64,0:52:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.50,0:52:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我…？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.66,0:53:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.32,0:53:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.64,0:53:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}电来了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.54,0:53:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶 小民
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.66,0:53:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你突然来厨房干嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.58,0:53:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对不起啊 我想做一层一层的便当给麻奈吃嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.28,0:53:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小民你在做菜啊…难道也是做便当？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.26,0:53:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我就觉得偶尔做做这个也能练习手艺
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.06,0:53:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就这样！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.90,0:53:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶…这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.68,0:53:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}难道说是Hokemon？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.12,0:53:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.96,0:53:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是Bricure
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.96,0:53:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs30\3c&H000000&\bord2}注：恶搞了《神奇宝贝》Pokemon和《光之美少女》Precure\N这里替换为了Hokke（多线鱼）与Buri（鰤鱼）
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.60,0:54:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这是人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.30,0:54:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你这人实在是！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.44,0:54:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.56,0:54:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.28,0:54:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}挺好的呀你看
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.32,0:54:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这炸鸡的大小正合麻奈的嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.08,0:54:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}颜色也搭配得挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.48,0:54:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}有红有黄
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.00,0:54:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}对…对了！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.62,0:54:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}居然还想到用鸡蛋丝做脸
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.44,0:54:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要是人类还真想不出来呢 Brecure
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.42,0:54:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}别说这个了！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.04,0:54:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不过你还真为麻奈着想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.56,0:54:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.44,0:54:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}作为一名厨师当然要考虑吃的人的感…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.46,0:54:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}那时候因为客人年长所以调味才比较重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.06,0:54:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}还有那次
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.84,0:54:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}明明是繁忙时的伙食…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.82,0:54:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可我却做得那么不方便吃
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.46,0:54:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我完全没有想到
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.02,0:54:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}吃的人的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.24,0:55:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.82,0:55:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小民？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.30,0:55:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.12,0:55:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}等便当做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.70,0:55:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}就要开始做新菜单！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.24,0:55:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}来帮我！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.30,0:55:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}诶 为什么是我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.14,0:55:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}就是你 反正很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.58,0:55:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真搞不懂她们是关系好还是不好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.02,0:55:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}哇 这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.90,0:55:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}吵死了 毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.42,0:55:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}又来
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.34,0:55:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}下次的新作就写…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.22,0:55:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}新人厨师！深夜的滑子菇汤！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.78,0:55:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这样的如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.34,0:55:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}再…再让我睡会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.76,0:56:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.68,0:56:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好臭！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.84,0:56:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}都烂成泥了…
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.92,0:56:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这原来是啥来着
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.98,0:56:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绪花不在可真不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.54,0:56:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}今天再不丢垃圾就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.66,0:56:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}来了来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.28,0:56:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}喂 松前家
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.62,0:56:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}大哥？好久不见~
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.56,0:56:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}很好啊 绪花也是
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.04,0:56:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.02,0:56:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}找到了赞助商
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.48,0:56:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可以办展会了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.64,0:57:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}到现在依然有人喜欢他的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.56,0:57:06.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.46,0:57:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}因为机会难得所以想把他私下拍的照片也展出来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.10,0:57:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我就想问问大哥那边还有没有他的照片留着
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.36,0:57:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我想就起绪花这名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.92,0:57:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.58,0:57:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}希望她长成跟花朵一样美丽的少女之类的意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.22,0:57:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯 也有这层意思
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.88,0:57:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但是在夏威夷语里面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.62,0:57:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是「家族」的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.14,0:57:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}OHANA
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.46,0:57:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}家族？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.88,0:57:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.88,0:57:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}家族
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.12,0:57:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}家族吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.44,0:57:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}嗯 我也喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.96,0:57:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好了 要拍了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.82,0:57:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}倒…倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.82,0:57:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.68,0:57:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我会再联系你的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.44,0:58:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好 请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.48,0:58:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不好…能不能赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.26,0:58:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没办法 跑吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.14,0:58:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}睡过头了！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.40,0:58:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小民 快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.50,0:58:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}绪花！等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.32,0:58:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}别跑 难得做的便当要挤坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.72,0:58:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}可是赶不上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.10,0:58:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}怎么了这么吵闹
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.48,0:58:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}今天也是一个好天
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.52,0:58:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}列车呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.58,0:58:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不行 还要30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.94,0:58:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}赶不上郊游了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.80,0:58:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小民等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.18,0:58:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}才不等
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.24,0:58:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}再不快点要迟到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.28,0:58:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.54,0:58:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}{\an8}抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.04,0:58:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.54,0:58:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真是太突然了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.30,0:58:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你是打算退居老家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.38,0:59:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我还没跟我母亲说
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.08,0:59:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}所以也不知道会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.00,0:59:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}总之尽量拜托看看
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.02,0:59:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}你先生的事情是很让人遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.46,0:59:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}但实在有点可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.24,0:59:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}难得你撰稿的工作才进入轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.82,0:59:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.64,0:59:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}真不好意思 等我安顿下来再跟您联系
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.32,0:59:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}先这样
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.38,0:59:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}乖乖
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.60,0:59:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小宝宝好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.34,0:59:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.36,0:59:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.24,0:59:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}上吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.66,0:59:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好久不见 豆丁爷
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.86,0:59:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}皋月…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.68,0:59:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这是皋月的孩子？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.60,1:00:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}她叫绪花
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.72,1:00:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}卷发啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.36,1:00:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我们家代代都是直发
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.36,1:00:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这点大概是像她爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.70,1:00:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}很可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.36,1:00:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.68,1:00:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}呐 妈妈在哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:24.14,1:00:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老板娘在…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.42,1:00:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.20,1:00:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}够了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.36,1:00:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.78,1:00:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}非常抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.14,1:00:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}都怪我搞错了客人点的菜
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.08,1:00:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}最近渔荒都没有什么好鱼…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.72,1:00:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}老板娘 找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.32,1:00:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}到处都说急着要也没多余的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.36,1:00:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我会负起责任！引咎辞职…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.50,1:00:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这要是你辞职能解决的问题我早就欣然让你辞职了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.18,1:00:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}这已经不是你一个人的问题
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.78,1:00:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}而是我们整个喜翠庄的问题
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.10,1:00:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}喜翠庄是我们
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.96,1:00:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}大伙儿的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.88,1:01:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}听好了
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.88,1:01:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}大家要一去度过这道难关
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.84,1:01:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好的！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.00,1:01:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}莲二 要做的事情还有很多
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.94,1:01:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}好的 抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.32,1:01:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.46,1:01:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我那时候完全没明白
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.68,1:01:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈她并不是纠结于父亲的亡灵
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.06,1:01:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不是沉醉在过去
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.50,1:01:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}妈妈她是…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.24,1:01:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}不能认输啊…
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.82,1:01:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}肯定是觉得不能认输吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.28,1:01:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}为了走向未来 一定不能输给自己
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.68,1:01:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}皋…皋月
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.58,1:01:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}别跟妈妈说我来过
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.70,1:01:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}要保重啊 豆丁爷
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.64,1:02:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}我怎么会输啊 死老太婆
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.28,1:02:18.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}开心吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.82,1:02:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.76,1:02:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}人生非得要快乐才行
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.30,1:02:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}是吧 绪花
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.66,1:02:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}走吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.78,1:02:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}等等！有垃圾！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.82,1:03:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be20}小菜！
